     * removed redundant #include´s
     % added to GetAsVariant/SetAsVariant checking for metaTable

  *  src/TIndex.prg
     * removed redundant #include´s

  *  src/TTable.prg
     * removed redundant #include´s
     * GetIndexName returns a empty string "" if there is no index
     + added ppty isMetaTable, this allows to late 'instantiate' a Table (open alias, check tablestruct, and
       create indexes), so building a linked table on TObjectFields don't will cause a infinite loop on tables
       with ciclic references on it (ie. table A has a object field B which has a object field of table A)
     + added method
       + CreateTableInstance: change status of metaTable
     * check by change metaTable status on GetIndex(),GetAlias(),GetDisplayFields()
     * renamed __DefineIndexes to __DefineSecondaryIndexes
     - removed WRITE clause to property Alias
     - removed SyncDetailsSources
     % small optmz on get/set Index object

  +  tests
  +  tests/test01.hbp
  +  tests/test01.prg
     + test to check for create tables with cicilic references


