     * renamed clause DEFAULT on ADD ... FIELD ... to DEFAULTVALUE
     * add clause NEWVALUE to ADD ... FIELD . the new value is used to populate field values when creating a new
       record, if there is not NEWVALUE then DEFAULTVALUE will be used then
     * add clause RJUST to DEFINE ... INDEX to right justify the key value on the index expression

